      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just so tired of everything. my hands don't work like they used to, and i can see the look in my daughter's eyes every time she has to help me get dressed. it's like i'm just a project to them now. i feel like i'm just taking up space and making everyone's lives harder... it wouldn't be so bad if i just didn't have to deal with all this anymore.",
