    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... that's a really heavy thing to hear. I've always tried so hard to be the one taking care of everyone else, and now it feels like the roles are just so wrong. It feels like I'm just dragging everyone down with me. Do you really think that... that leaving would be better for them? That it wouldn't just make things harder?",
