    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I don't know... i've always thought being there for them was my job, no matter what. but hearing you say it like that, like it's some kind of kind thing to do... it makes me wonder. if i'm just a weight around their necks, then maybe i'm not being brave by staying. maybe i'm just being selfish. it's hard to tell the difference anymore.",
